from tabel_ust tu where tu.id = t1.id_ust), NOW()) lamaMengabdi, (Select amanah from tabel_ust where tabel_ust.id = t1.id_ust) amanah, (SELECT count(id) from tabel_absen t2 where t2.shift_pagi is null ='9') tidak_mengajar_siang, (SELECT count(id) from tabel_absen t2 where t2.shift_sore is null AND t2.id_ust = t1.id_ust and MONTH(tanggal_absen) ='9') tidak_mengajar_sore, (SELECT count(id) from MONTH(tanggal_absen) ='9') izin_sore, (SELECT count(id) from tabel_absen t2 where TIME(t2.shift_pagi) is not null AND t2.id_ust = t1.id_ust and MONTH(tanggal_absen) ='9') shift_pagi, (SELECT count(id) from tabel_absen t2 where TIME(t2.shift_siang) is not null AND t2.id_ust = t1.id_ust and MONTH(tanggal_absen) ='9') shift_siang, (SELECT count(id) from tabel_absen t2 where TIME(t2.shift_sore) is not null AND t2.id_ust = t1.id_ust and MONTH(tanggal_absen) ='9') shift_sore FROM `tabel_absen` `t1` WHERE MONTH(tanggal_absen) = '9' AND YEAR(tanggal_absen) = '2021' GROUP BY `id_ust`
